    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next adventure, this is the one. Come take it for a spin, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
