      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1987 Porsche 911 Carrera is a superlative example of the G-Series evolution, featuring the highly desirable Getrag G50 five-speed transaxle with Borg-Warner synchronizers for precise, tactile gear selection. Powered by a robust 3.2-liter air-cooled flat-six, the powerplant utilizes Bosch Motronic DME engine management to deliver linear power delivery and exceptional throttle response. The chassis maintains factory-spec integrity, utilizing longitudinal torsion bars and semi-trailing arms for the communicative feedback synonymous with this platform. The mechanical condition is peerless: the top end is dry, valve clearances are dialed to factory tolerances, and the four-piston calipers provide immediate bite against ventilated rotors. Sitting on staggered 16-inch Fuchs forged alloy wheels, this vehicle exhibits zero driveline lash and remains a turn-key acquisition for the air-cooled purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2022 model. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Original paint. Interior flawless. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a factory-fresh luster on its flawless paintwork with zero imperfections, chips, or swirl marks. The interior is a time capsule, featuring supple, uncreased leather upholstery that still retains its original showroom scent. Every button, switch, and digital display functions with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach; it has been serviced exclusively by master technicians using original equipment manufacturer parts, with a full, documented history that leaves nothing to chance. From the pristine alloy wheels wrapped in premium rubber to the spotless engine bay, every inch of this machine reflects a lifetime of obsessive care. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen ready for its next discerning owner. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
